44:11.440 --> 44:13.715
I love you guys.

44:13.800 --> 44:15.791
This is fun.

44:16.840 --> 44:20.753
So anyway, what you're saying,

44:20.840 --> 44:24.150
I'm the Man, "Whitey",

44:24.600 --> 44:32.075
and you guys are the victims of
a tyrannical, racist, oppressive society?

44:32.160 --> 44:33.991
That's right, man.

44:34.360 --> 44:36.351
Man, that sucks!

44:39.080 --> 44:41.878
I'm gonna talk to some people
and straighten this out,

44:41.960 --> 44:44.633
cos this is a bunch of bullcrap!

44:44.720 --> 44:47.917
- All right?
- Yeah!

44:48.000 --> 44:51.470
- I'm gonna go get 'em.
- Kick ass, Whitey!

44:57.320 --> 45:00.949
- So when do I go on?
- Six, seven minutes. Just relax.

45:01.040 --> 45:03.474
- All right, all right.
- Straighten your tie.

45:03.560 --> 45:06.358
- Should I lose the tie?
- Loosen the tie.

45:06.440 --> 45:09.079
Just take it down. Take it down.

45:16.720 --> 45:19.188
Yeah!

45:21.160 --> 45:23.515
All right!

45:23.600 --> 45:25.113
Whoo!

45:25.200 --> 45:28.317
Yeah, man! I love you guys!

45:28.400 --> 45:31.437
- Whoa, whoa. Hang on. All right.
- Excellent!

45:31.520 --> 45:34.353
- What's your name?
- Mike Donnelly.

45:35.160 --> 45:38.118
Governor Donnelly? Nice threads.

45:38.200 --> 45:41.351
- No, you jag, he ain't the governor.
- He's runnin'for governor.

45:41.440 --> 45:45.558
- Well, get on out there!
- No! No! You got the wrong guy.

45:45.720 --> 45:47.995
Just a second. Fellas, come on.

45:55.640 --> 45:57.631
Uh...

46:03.680 --> 46:05.352
Um...

46:05.440 --> 46:08.193
I'm not supposed to be here. Uh...

46:13.120 --> 46:15.873
God. What is this?

46:18.480 --> 46:20.311
l, uh...

46:20.400 --> 46:23.995
I could sure use some cupcakes
or peanut-butter cups about now!

46:24.080 --> 46:26.719
- (riotous cheering)
- Yeah!

46:26.800 --> 46:30.554
- You know what that's about!
- (whoops of approval)

46:30.640 --> 46:34.315
So I guess you guys should vote,
you know, because...

46:34.400 --> 46:37.312
voting kicks ass, right? Yeah!

46:38.160 --> 46:43.837
And let me tell you, if you're gonna vote,
why not vote for Al Donnelly, right?

46:43.920 --> 46:46.115
(cheering)

46:48.400 --> 46:50.630
(synchronised drumrolls)

46:53.360 --> 46:56.796
Cos if voting kicks ass...

46:56.880 --> 46:59.235
What in the hell...

46:59.320 --> 47:00.992
Oh, please, God, I'm dreaming.

47:01.320 --> 47:03.515
...you've got some kick-ass shit!

47:09.080 --> 47:12.117
Oh, God. I'm a dead man. Oh!

47:12.200 --> 47:15.317
I'm hyperventilating... Oh! Oh!

47:17.440 --> 47:19.829
Cos I was born in the USA.

47:22.120 --> 47:24.190
(shouts of "Yeah!")

47:26.400 --> 47:30.678
You gotta fight for your right to vote.

47:40.160 --> 47:44.358
That's one small step for man,
one giant...

47:45.920 --> 47:48.309
- I have a dream!
- (cheering)

47:55.000 --> 47:56.911
Power to the people!

48:01.760 --> 48:03.796
Burn <i>, </i> baby <i>, </i> burn!

48:03.880 --> 48:05.518
Oh, Mike!

48:07.400 --> 48:09.391
Hey, fellas. Yeah.

48:10.280 --> 48:12.077
Kill Whitey!

48:12.160 --> 48:13.957
(stunned silence)

48:15.440 --> 48:17.874
