01:09:37.600 --> 01:09:42.116
Jesus. Did it ever occur to you family
may be more important than career?

01:09:42.399 --> 01:09:45.710
Ever occur to you that at some point
you'll have to make a choice

01:09:45.800 --> 01:09:48.029
between me and your loser brother?

01:10:12.520 --> 01:10:15.353
Go and scope it out.
Nobody's gonna recognise you.

01:10:15.440 --> 01:10:18.034
OK. Promise me you'll stay right here.

01:10:24.160 --> 01:10:26.549
Thank you. Thank you very much.

01:10:27.800 --> 01:10:31.509
This election was about
the majesty of democracy,

01:10:31.920 --> 01:10:35.549
where the gathered masses
held their vote high.

01:10:35.640 --> 01:10:37.232
(applause)

01:10:41.160 --> 01:10:45.631
My re-election would not have been
possible without the people in this state

01:10:45.720 --> 01:10:48.188
who supported me in this victory.

01:10:48.280 --> 01:10:51.397
I must also thank
my wonderful husband Dennis

01:10:51.480 --> 01:10:54.597
and my two beautiful,
intelligent children...

01:10:54.680 --> 01:10:57.797
Psst! Steve. I'm in.

01:10:59.640 --> 01:11:02.393
Where the hell's Drake?
He's supposed to be here.

01:11:02.480 --> 01:11:06.393
I'm surprised we can't count on a guy
whose bus is surrounded by mines.

01:11:06.480 --> 01:11:08.471
All right. Here's what we do.

01:11:11.240 --> 01:11:13.151
We dress as caterers, right?

01:11:13.240 --> 01:11:17.074
Nobody looks at a caterer's face.
It's always "Whaddaya got in the tray?"

01:11:17.160 --> 01:11:20.277
Then we sneak around back.
When Tracy starts to...

01:11:21.160 --> 01:11:23.833
Something's happening here.
Steve, help.

01:11:23.920 --> 01:11:25.114
Steve.

01:11:25.200 --> 01:11:27.156
Steve, get back here.

01:11:27.240 --> 01:11:30.312
Oh, my God.
The damn thing's caught in my belt.

01:11:30.400 --> 01:11:33.039
God! Help, please!

01:11:35.000 --> 01:11:36.911
- I can't...
- (gasps)

01:11:38.200 --> 01:11:39.679
I can't... God!

01:11:40.080 --> 01:11:42.389
- You in the band, help.
- Hello.

01:11:42.480 --> 01:11:44.277
Help!

01:11:45.000 --> 01:11:46.433
God!

01:11:47.360 --> 01:11:49.555
- Stay.
- Steve! Help.

01:11:49.640 --> 01:11:52.029
- How are you?
- Steve! Please!

01:11:52.120 --> 01:11:54.554
Somebody! Somebody help me.

01:11:54.640 --> 01:11:56.995
Somebody help me!

01:11:57.240 --> 01:11:59.959
Agh! Help!

01:12:01.560 --> 01:12:06.918
The voters have spoken, and I have
heard their message loud and clear.

01:12:07.000 --> 01:12:09.560
- And that message is...
- (Mike) God! Help!

01:12:09.640 --> 01:12:12.598
- Holy shit!
- (shocked gasps)

01:12:14.560 --> 01:12:16.835
(laughs nervously)

01:12:18.280 --> 01:12:20.635
Hi, there. Hi.

01:12:20.840 --> 01:12:23.957
Boy, I feel like a horse's patoot.

01:12:26.200 --> 01:12:27.599
l, uh...

01:12:27.680 --> 01:12:31.036
Oh, no! For the love of God!

01:12:32.080 --> 01:12:34.833
Aaaarrggh!

01:12:43.520 --> 01:12:46.239
(groans)

01:12:46.320 --> 01:12:49.198
I'm all right. I'm OK.

01:12:49.280 --> 01:12:51.748
Gimme a minute.
Gimme a minute. I'll be fine.

01:12:52.760 --> 01:12:56.070
Nobody move, or Steve Dodds gets it!

01:12:56.160 --> 01:12:57.718
- Who?
- Steve Dodds.

01:12:57.800 --> 01:13:00.598
- Who's this guy?
- From the Donnelly campaign.

01:13:00.680 --> 01:13:03.399
What does it matter?
He's got a gun! You're a cop.

01:13:03.480 --> 01:13:07.109
Get over here. I'll kill him! I'll kill him!

01:13:07.200 --> 01:13:11.432
- I want that asshole taken out.
- I'll get a sharpshooter on it right away.

01:13:11.520 --> 01:13:14.637
- Get your ass up there.
- Ow!

01:13:14.720 --> 01:13:19.555
Everybody back up,
or I blow the pipsqueak's head off.

01:13:19.640 --> 01:13:21.790
I've got somethin' to say!

01:13:21.880 --> 01:13:25.634
Please listen to him. Do what he says.
I have children. Tommy and Sally...

01:13:25.720 --> 01:13:27.119
- Shut up!
- All right.

01:13:27.440 --> 01:13:29.954
You keep your mouth shut, squirt.

01:13:30.040 --> 01:13:32.508
As soon as you get a clear shot, take it.

01:13:32.600 --> 01:13:37.435
(Mike) OK, listen up.
This is serious business.

01:13:38.320 --> 01:13:43.155
Now, we've all been screwed
by Governor Tracy.

01:13:43.240 --> 01:13:45.549
And now I'm gonna screw her!

01:13:45.640 --> 01:13:46.834
(shocked gasps)

01:13:46.920 --> 01:13:52.756
I mean, I have evidence here you need
to know about now before it's too late.

01:13:52.840 --> 01:13:55.638
- Mike. Mike, what are you doing here?
- Oh, man.

01:13:56.360 --> 01:13:59.591
- Isn't that Steve Dodds?
- Uh, yes, sir.

01:13:59.680 --> 01:14:03.514
Al, man, I know what I'm doin'.
I'm gonna prove you won the election.

01:14:03.600 --> 01:14:06.717
Mike, put the gun down.
There's other ways to handle this.

01:14:07.000 --> 01:14:11.516
No, man! Al, there's no other way!
You gotta believe me.

01:14:11.600 --> 01:14:14.592
I believe you.
I just don't want you to get hurt.

01:14:15.120 --> 01:14:20.035
Look, I know this looks bad.
Al, man, I'm not a screwup on this one.

01:14:20.120 --> 01:14:22.759
I've got proof this time. Real proof.

01:14:23.680 --> 01:14:26.592
(Al) But the election's over. It's history.

01:14:26.680 --> 01:14:29.148
Like you're gonna be
if you don't put that gun down.

01:14:29.240 --> 01:14:31.629
Al, please!

01:14:32.480 --> 01:14:36.234
If you love me like a brother,
you gotta back me up on this.

01:14:36.320 --> 01:14:39.915
All right, Mike. I'll back you up.
What do you want me to do?

01:14:40.000 --> 01:14:42.150
Just let me explain what happened.

01:14:43.200 --> 01:14:45.509
- Oh!
- (crowd scream)

01:14:46.080 --> 01:14:50.039
That's it. Game over.
I'm not even getting paid for this.

01:14:50.320 --> 01:14:53.596
- This is not worth it.
- Look out. Look out. Look out.

01:14:53.680 --> 01:14:55.477
OK.

01:14:56.280 --> 01:14:58.271
(crowd scream)

01:14:58.600 --> 01:15:02.878
Mr Thunder-maker here is gonna start
barkin' fire if you don't stop moving

01:15:02.960 --> 01:15:05.520
and listen to what
this young man has to say.

01:15:06.160 --> 01:15:08.071
Go ahead, Mike. Clear.

01:15:08.400 --> 01:15:12.996
Thank you, sir. You've just met Drake
Sabitch, a great American soldier.

01:15:13.080 --> 01:15:16.356
I'd like to tell you about
some other great American soldiers.

01:15:16.440 --> 01:15:18.874
Drake Sabitch's grandfather,
Winston Sabitch,

01:15:18.960 --> 01:15:21.918
whose name you'll find
at the top of this list.

01:15:22.000 --> 01:15:26.869
It says that he registered
and voted for Governor Tracy.

01:15:26.960 --> 01:15:30.077
- We're proud to have him as a voter.
- Hold your tongue, wench.

01:15:30.160 --> 01:15:34.233
The fact is Winston Sabitch was killed
in the Argonne Forest in 1918.

01:15:34.320 --> 01:15:38.472
A zeppelin landed on his head,
smashing his head clean out of his ass.

01:15:38.560 --> 01:15:41.518
That's my granddad. Rest in pieces, sir.

01:15:42.800 --> 01:15:46.315
Norris Sabitch met his maker
in Iwo Jima, 1944.

01:15:46.720 --> 01:15:51.236
Nelson Sabitch was killed
near the 38th Parallel in Korea.

01:15:51.320 --> 01:15:56.110
But yesterday these men managed
to cast their vote for Evelyn Tracy.

01:15:56.200 --> 01:15:58.589
(disapproving murmurs)

01:15:58.680 --> 01:16:01.148
You heard it here, folks. Voter fraud.

01:16:05.240 --> 01:16:09.074
Half these people are buried in the
Garfield cemetery. That's one county.

01:16:09.160 --> 01:16:13.676
- It's probably the same statewide.
- Hold on just a minute, young fellow.

01:16:13.760 --> 01:16:17.673
There's a perfectly good explanation
for all of this. Neuschwander.

01:16:18.600 --> 01:16:24.197
Actually, there is a perfectly
good explanation for this.

01:16:24.680 --> 01:16:27.558
- She put us up to it.
- Would you shut up?!

01:16:27.640 --> 01:16:29.437
- It's all her.
- Shut up!

01:16:32.880 --> 01:16:36.077
Ladies and gentlemen,
this young man is a fine patriot.

01:16:36.160 --> 01:16:38.720
He deserves to be hoisted up
on our shoulders.

01:16:38.800 --> 01:16:41.360
- Sergeant, please. This isn't necessary.
- Come on.

01:16:41.440 --> 01:16:43.795
- Oh, you're a large American.
- Argh!

01:16:46.080 --> 01:16:47.911
Get off of me.

01:16:48.920 --> 01:16:52.515
My foot's caught a little bit.
I'm sorry. I beg your pardon.

01:16:52.600 --> 01:16:56.639
- I'm asking you to get off me!
