01:16:56.720 --> 01:16:59.518
I'm just trying to get
a little leverage on my foot.

01:16:59.600 --> 01:17:01.397
Agh!

01:17:03.880 --> 01:17:07.475
- No, no, no! Please, somebody help me!
- Oh, man.

01:17:07.560 --> 01:17:09.551
(grunting)

01:17:11.480 --> 01:17:15.678
- OK. Hi, how are ya?
